					</p>
				</statement>
				<choices randomize="yes">
					<choice correct="yes">
						<statement>True</statement>
						<feedback>
							<p>
								Correct! Computing the derivatives, you get <me>e^{8x},\quad 8e^{8x},\quad 64e^{8x},\quad 512e^{8x}</me>, which are all like-terms.
							</p>
						</feedback>
					</choice>
					<choice correct="no"><statement>False</statement><feedback>Incorrect.</feedback></choice>
				</choices>
			</task>
			<task label="exponential-solns-cyu-2">
				<title><e component="emoji">ü§îüí≠</e> Select the Exponential Solutions</title>
				<statement>
					<p>
						The differential equation
						<me>
							y'' - 4y = 0
						</me>,
						has which of the following exponential solutions? <em>(Select all that Apply)</em>
					</p>
					<p/>
				</statement>
				<areas>
					<sidebyside>
						<p/>
						<p><area><m>e^{-2x}</m></area></p>
						<p><area><m>e^{2x}</m></area></p>
						<p><area correct="no"><m>xe^{2x}</m></area></p>
						<p><area correct="no"><m>e^{4x}</m></area></p>
						<p><area correct="no"><m>e^{x}</m></area></p>
						<p><area correct="no"><m>e^{-4x}</m></area></p>
					</sidebyside>
					<p/>
				</areas>
				<feedback>
					<p>Hint: The characteristic equation is <m>r^2 - 4 = 0</m>.</p>
				</feedback>
			</task>
		</exercise>

	</subsection>

</section>
